====Usage notes====
* Within the French language (which has no [[phonemic]] [[aspirate]]s) this usually refers to the loss of an [[h aspiré]], which allows {{l|fr|liaison|liaisons}} to occur: e.g. des haricot, normally pronounced /de a.ʁi.ko/, becomes /de.z‿a.ʁi.ko/.
